            , were indicted for <rs id="t17830226-72-off385" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830226-72-off385" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830226-72-off385" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17830226-72-cd386" type="crimeDate">19th of February </rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830226-72-off385 t17830226-72-cd386"></join>last, one live hog, value 16 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830226-72-victim766" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Burley
                  <interp inst="t17830226-72-victim766" type="surname" value="Burley"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830226-72-victim766" type="given" value="James"></interp>
